  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0003",
    "kind": "visual_panel",
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678",
    "primary_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_12",
    "source": "visual_seed",
    "member_count": 11,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_2",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "昆曲兴起于元代后期，在明代中期至清代前期发展到极盛。 清代中叶以后，昆曲因脱离现实、因循守旧而由盛转衰。",
        "bbox": [
          0.34099153567110035,
          0.294712840245119,
          0.8778718258766627,
          0.3329058001995155
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "昆曲是融诗、乐、歌、舞、戏为一体的戏剧艺术形式，对京 剧、越剧等大部分后起剧种都产生过深刻影响。昆曲在新中国获得 了新生。",
        "bbox": [
          0.3401854091092302,
          0.33689610944848225,
          0.8786779524385329,
          0.3956106598261365
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "代表性的昆曲剧作主要有汤显祖的《牡丹亭》、洪升的《长 生殿》以及孔尚任的《桃花扇》等。",
        "bbox": [
          0.34099153567110035,
          0.400741057431951,
          0.8786779524385329,
          0.4395040615647713
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "昆曲又称昆腔，在20世纪初称为昆剧，是中国最古 的剧种之。",
        "bbox": [
          0.33937928254735994,
          0.546102322930027,
          0.8778718258766627,
          0.586005415419695
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "元代后期，江苏昆带流以当地为基础的南 曲，明初称“昆腔”。明嘉靖年间，昆曲已发展成为雅俗 共赏的戏曲形式。昆魏良辅对昆腔进新,创造出曲调 清丽委婉的“磨腔”，并迅速流传开来，魏良辅因此被称",
        "bbox": [
          0.3385731559854897,
          0.5905657688470857,
          0.8802902055622733,
          0.6766424397890837
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_12",
        "observed_type": "image_body",
        "canon_role": "picture",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.38129786376461106,
          0.6874732791791364,
          0.8367593712212817,
          0.9052301553370387
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "“昆曲”之带唱带 做，实为旧日之载歌载 舞……许多听不懂曲子 的人，有时也可看出一 部分情节，应当是表 情动作上有所帮助之 故……",
        "bbox": [
          0.09189842805320435,
          0.7193957531708708,
          0.28698105602579604,
          0.8601966652415562
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_678_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "—周贻白：",
        "bbox": [
          0.19830713422007254,
          0.8664671512042184,
          0.28214429665457474,
          0.8790081231295426
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
